### =====================================================================
### SimCard API  (base route: api/Sim/)
### TagSimOperator: 1 IranCell, 2 HamrahAvval, 3 Rigthel, 5 Shatel
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Create - full
POST {{host}}/api/Sim/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "number": "09120000000",
  "serial": "SN-0001",
  "tags": [2]
}

### Create - number only
POST {{host}}/api/Sim/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "number": "09350000000",
  "tags": [1]
}

### Read
POST {{host}}/api/Sim/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "tags": [1],
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Update
POST {{host}}/api/Sim/Update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "serial": "SN-0002"
}

### Delete
POST {{host}}/api/Sim/Delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}
